{"type": "article", "id": 3747, "title": "Balsam 系列靠枕", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-21T08:09:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060523324497jkdqBiOMLynwNQ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t2007 年，两位美国设计师 Neil Rasmus 与 Richard Brandt 在纽约创立了生活用品品牌 IZOLA，他们主张即便是最普通的日常生活用品，也应该有着细节上的巧思。日前，IZOLA 推出了 2014 秋冬系列名为「Balsam」的靠枕，设计团队选用了 100% 的棉麻织物作为靠枕的外套，内部则装满了香脂冷杉的针叶，透出淡雅清香的味道。在外部的棉麻织物表层，印有「NEW YORK」「IT WILL WARM YOU TWICE」等复古风格的字体。定价 24－32 美元不等，<a href=\"http://store.hypebeast.com/brands/izola?utm_source=Hypebeast.com&amp;utm_medium=Editorial%20Post&amp;utm_campaign=IZOLA%202014%20Fall%2FWinter%20Balsam%20Pillows\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233243jxmErJ21HAhn7zCs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233244TvKnMsbOeoW8Jxt0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}